data.description: NO HOA! Grand 2-story Great Rm entrance w/ laminate wood thru-out main. You'll love the see-thru fireplace which can be enjoyed from 3 sides. Home has been freshly painted. Kitchen features granite countertops & Stainless appliances. Primary Bed on main w/ new LVP flooring in the Bathroom. Brand new carpet upstairs! Upstairs loft could be used as an office or recreation/play room. Nice size secondary bedrooms including a walk-in closet. Garage has attached shelving "PLUS" a 50 AMP LEVEL 2 CHARGER W A STANDARD J1772 PLUG FOR EV CHARGING! Fresh Seed & Straw around the exterior.! Fridge, Washer & Dryer Included!  Another added bonus is the Secure Package Drop Box bolted to the front porch. Water Heater replaced about three years ago. Great value for the price!
